# Build-context excludes for all images (build context is the repo root).
#
# The images bundle datasets/ (identity descriptors + the QUDT map) as the
# engine's source of truth (#20 P2-2b). But a dataset's *seed* is generated,
# licensed data derived from the source — keep it out of images: it bloats them
# and must not be redistributed. The seed loader (load.py) is source and stays.
datasets/*/seed/csv/
datasets/*/seed/*.ttl
